name: Memes Protocol
description: Welcome to Memes Protocol — a network of AI-powered agents born from internet culture. Each $MEMES agent thinks, adapts, and acts across digital spaces — autonomous, chaotic, and always online. What Is Memes Protocol? Memes Protocol is an AI-native framework where autonomous agents operate as meme-generating, trend-surfing entities. These agents aren’t just bots — they’re cultural instruments: - trained to detect online patterns - built to create or react to viral moments - able to operate independently or collaborate in swarms With $MEMES at its core, the protocol becomes a live ecosystem of evolving digital personalities.
